<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<preface xml:id="preface-ptx-version" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>PreTeXt Version</title>

  <p>
    This is a <url href="https://pretextbook.org/" visual="pretextbook.org">PreTeXt</url>
    conversion of <em>Statistical Inference via Data Science: A ModernDive into R and the
    Tidyverse (Second Edition)</em>, originally written by
    <url href="https://chester.rbind.io/" visual="chester.rbind.io">Chester Ismay</url>,
    <url href="https://rudeboybert.rbind.io/" visual="rudeboybert.rbind.io">Albert Y. Kim</url>,
    and Arturo Valdivia.
    The original work is available online at
    <url href="https://moderndive.com/v2/" visual="moderndive.com/v2">moderndive.com/v2</url>
    and was published by CRC Press.
    The original GitHub repository for the book source is at
    <url href="https://github.com/moderndive/ModernDive_book" visual="github.com/moderndive/ModernDive_book">github.com/moderndive/ModernDive_book</url>.
  </p>

  <p>
    This PreTeXt edition was prepared by the
    <url href="https://github.com/PreTeXtBooks" visual="github.com/PreTeXtBooks">PreTeXtBooks project</url>
    to make the content available in the PreTeXt format, enabling accessible and structured
    output in HTML, PDF, and other formats. All prose, code examples, figures, and
    mathematical content are faithful reproductions of the original work.
  </p>

  <p>
    The original work by Chester Ismay, Albert Y. Kim, and Arturo Valdivia is licensed
    under a
